        Parameters:
        createCount - Number of times to perform a create operation
        readCount - Number of times to perform a read operation
        updateCount - Number of times to perform an update operation
        deleteCount - Number of times to perform a delete operation
        nodeCount - Number of nodes to create
        rejectionProbability - Probability of rejecting a PENDING operation
        updateProbability - Probability of changing a field during an update operation
        trialCount - Number of trials to perform
        abbreviatedFactor - Divisor for adjusting counts when doing abbreviated testing
        stressedFactor - Multiplier for sdjusting counts when doing stress testing
        abbreviated - Flag to indicate whether to do abbreviated testing
        stressed - Flag to indicate whether to to stress testing
        assessCountConsistency - Flag to check the object count consistency between nodes
        assessContentConsistency - Flag to check the object value consistency between nodes
        assessValidity - Flag to check the validity of the CRDT values at each node
        assessOperationCountConsistency - Flag to check the operation count consistency between the nodes
